---
/**
 * Slide 09 v2 · Healthcare. Closing slide; full-bleed treatment, serif crescendo.
 */
const id = 'healthcare';
---

<section data-slot="09" data-variant="editorial" id={id} class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 bg-indigo-950 dark:bg-black vibrant:bg-black snap-start">
  <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-xs tracking-widest font-mono text-stone-50/40 vibrant:text-orange-500">09 / 09</span>

  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-8">What's Next</p>

  <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl text-stone-50 leading-[1.04] tracking-tight max-w-5xl mb-10">
    The Apprenticeship Degree is moving <em class="not-italic text-orange-500">beyond teaching.</em>
  </h2>
  <p class="font-serif italic text-xl md:text-2xl text-stone-50/85 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mb-16">
    Reach just launched the <span class="not-italic font-semibold text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500">Apprenticeship College of Health</span> — in partnership with the Training Fund — to address national healthcare workforce shortages.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl">
    <div class="border-l-2 border-orange-500 pl-6 py-2">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-3">Leadership</p>
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-50 mb-1">Dr. Metoka Welch</p>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-sm text-stone-50/65">Executive Dean, Apprenticeship College of Health</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-orange-500 pl-6 py-2">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-3">Press</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 font-serif text-sm text-stone-50/85">
        <li><span class="italic">"A College for Health Care Apprentices"</span> · Inside Higher Ed</li>
        <li><span class="italic">"A Pioneer of Apprenticeship Degrees Steps Into Healthcare"</span> · Work Shift</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl border-t border-stone-50/20 pt-8">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-4">Why this matters</p>
    <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl italic text-stone-50 leading-snug">
      The expansion validates the original thesis: the model is <span class="not-italic font-semibold text-orange-500">sector-agnostic.</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-12 font-serif text-base italic text-stone-50/75 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
    "Apprenticeship degrees can remedy crucial skill shortages, reduce the cost of higher education, and create more opportunities for more Americans."
  </p>
</section>
